---
title: Job observation processing lifecycle
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Received

    Received --> Normalizing: worker starts
    Normalizing --> Normalized: versioned interpretation persisted
    Normalizing --> Failed: processing error

    Normalized --> Resolving: identity resolution starts
    Resolving --> Resolved: existing or new canonical identity
    Resolving --> Ambiguous: safe automatic decision unavailable
    Resolving --> Failed: processing error

    Failed --> Normalizing: retry normalization
    Failed --> Resolving: retry resolution when normalization exists
    Ambiguous --> Resolving: new evidence or human review

    Resolved --> [*]

    note right of Received
        Source evidence is immutable.
        Processing knowledge may advance.
    end note

    note right of Ambiguous
        Valid outcome, not failure.
        No canonical association is forced.
    end note
